To opt out of the sale or sharing of your personal information relating to cookies, move the toggle to the left and select "Confirm My Choice". If you choose to opt out of this data sharing, you will still see ads, though they may be less relevant to you. These ads may be based on historical information or information shared or sold by other sources. You will need to renew this choice each time you clear your cookies or use a new browser or device. This opt-out applies only to certain cookie (“online”) data we have about you. If you wish to communicate your opt out choices with respect to selling or sharing other types of data beyond cookies (e.g., “offline” data) you may do so via "Your Privacy Choices" link in the footer of this website.', 'Your Privacy Choices', 'In order to provide you with free high-quality content that you love to watch and offers that are more relevant to you, the National Football League collects and shares certain personal information.

If you choose to opt out of these cookies, you will still see ads, though they may be less relevant to you.

For more information about how we collect and share your personal information and other privacy choices you may have, refer to our
            ']
